content: This would definitely benefit from a checklist system and the ability to change out the bundle items since the 1.5 update allows you to remix bundles. I would've rated higher, but there's a surprising lack of heart event info for the non-marriage residents, so that would be another thing to fix. Still, for a project not yet a month old, this is promising to be well worth the purchase. Looking forward to later development and maybe a star or two more as the product improves.
Quite nice it has what i need, it would be nice if the letters are a bit larger, it would also be nice if you can add information about the theater, I hope you continue on updating the app!
Wouldn't open half the time. When it did it didn't seem to have half the items you could actually craft so unfortunately it's a no from me
